            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>lime[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Add your <strong>mayo </strong>to a small bowl with a small squeeze of <strong>lime juice</strong>, a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and plenty of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>lime mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1681919071709-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1681919071709-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
