            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Cajun-style rice</strong>  topped with the <strong>spiced basa pieces</strong> and drizzle over the<strong> lime mayo</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>lime wedges</strong> and season with <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
